[
  "div",
  {
    "className": "content-wrapper"
  },
  [
    "h1",
    {},
    "Degrees of Adjectives"
  ],
  [
    "p",
    {},
    [
      "In Greek, adjectives change their form to indicate intensity. There are three degrees: ",
      [
        "strong",
        {},
        "Positive"
      ],
      " (tall), ",
      [
        "strong",
        {},
        "Comparative"
      ],
      " (taller), and ",
      [
        "strong",
        {},
        "Superlative"
      ],
      " (tallest)."
    ]
  ],
  [
    "h2",
    {},
    "1. The Positive Degree (Θετικός)"
  ],
  [
    "p",
    {},
    "This is the base form of the adjective as learned in the previous lesson."
  ],
  [
    "ul",
    {
      "className": "phrase-list"
    },
    [
      "li",
      {},
      [
        "span",
        {
          "className": "spanish"
        },
        "ωραίος"
      ],
      [
        "span",
        {
          "className": "meaning"
        },
        "beautiful"
      ]
    ],
    [
      "li",
      {},
      [
        "span",
        {
          "className": "spanish"
        },
        "καλός"
      ],
      [
        "span",
        {
          "className": "meaning"
        },
        "good"
      ]
    ]
  ],
  [
    "h2",
    {},
    "2. The Comparative Degree (Συγκριτικός)"
  ],
  [
    "p",
    {},
    "There are two ways to form the comparative in Greek:"
  ],
  [
    "div",
    {
      "className": "content-grid mt-8"
    },
    [
      "h3",
      {},
      "Method A: Using \"πιο\""
    ],
    [
      "p",
      {},
      [
        "Simply place the word ",
        [
          "strong",
          {},
          "πιο"
        ],
        " (more) before the adjective. This works for almost all adjectives."
      ]
    ]
  ],
  [
    "div",
    {
      "className": "example-box"
    },
    [
      "p",
      {},
      "πιο ωραίος more beautiful / handsomer"
    ]
  ],
  [
    "h3",
    {},
    "Method B: Using Suffixes"
  ],
  [
    "p",
    {},
    [
      "Add the suffix ",
      [
        "strong",
        {},
        "-ότερος"
      ],
      " to the root of the adjective."
    ]
  ],
  [
    "div",
    {
      "className": "example-box"
    },
    [
      "p",
      {},
      [
        "ωραι ",
        [
          "strong",
          {},
          "ότερος"
        ],
        " more beautiful"
      ]
    ]
  ],
  [
    "h2",
    {},
    "3. The Superlative Degree (Υπεθετικός)"
  ],
  [
    "div",
    {
      "className": "table-container"
    },
    [
      "table",
      {},
      [
        "thead",
        {},
        [
          "tr",
          {},
          [
            "th",
            {},
            "Type"
          ],
          [
            "th",
            {},
            "Formation"
          ],
          [
            "th",
            {},
            "Example"
          ]
        ]
      ],
      [
        "tbody",
        {},
        [
          "tr",
          {},
          [
            "td",
            {},
            [
              [
                "strong",
                {},
                "Relative"
              ]
            ]
          ],
          [
            "td",
            {},
            "Article + \"πιο\" + Adj"
          ],
          [
            "td",
            {},
            "ο πιο ωραίος (the most beautiful)"
          ]
        ],
        [
          "tr",
          {},
          [
            "td",
            {},
            [
              [
                "strong",
                {},
                "Absolute"
              ]
            ]
          ],
          [
            "td",
            {},
            [
              "Add ",
              [
                "strong",
                {},
                "-ότατος"
              ]
            ]
          ],
          [
            "td",
            {},
            [
              "ωραι ",
              [
                "strong",
                {},
                "ότατος"
              ],
              " (very beautiful)"
            ]
          ]
        ]
      ]
    ]
  ],
  [
    "div",
    {
      "className": "info-box mt-12 mb-12"
    },
    [
      "h3",
      {},
      "Common Irregulars"
    ],
    [
      "p",
      {},
      "Some adjectives have unique comparative forms:"
    ],
    [
      "ul",
      {
        "className": "phrase-list"
      },
      [
        "li",
        {},
        [
          "span",
          {
            "className": "spanish"
          },
          "καλός → καλύτερος"
        ],
        [
          "span",
          {
            "className": "meaning"
          },
          "better"
        ]
      ],
      [
        "li",
        {},
        [
          "span",
          {
            "className": "spanish"
          },
          "μεγάλος → μεγαλύτερος"
        ],
        [
          "span",
          {
            "className": "meaning"
          },
          "bigger"
        ]
      ]
    ]
  ]
]